What is a ROS 2 Node?
Subprogram in your application, responsible for only one thing
- Combined into a graph
- Comm with each other thrugh topics, services, and params
- Befentis:
- Reduce Code complexity
- Fault tolerance
- Can be written in Python, C++ and communicate without problem2
